&lt;p&gt;    Fixes &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-4765&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-4765&lt;/a&gt; by simply using artificially broken hosts that are not resolved as potential collisions (127.0.53.53s) by some DNS servers.&lt;/p&gt;

